Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
endECO(25.10)                                                    endECO(25.10)

Name
       endECO - Ends logging ECO operations

Syntax
       endECO

       [-help]

       Ends logging ECO operations.

Parameters
       None

Examples
              * The following commands show the usage of initECO and endECO.

                initECO   <FILE1>ecoAddRepeater  -net  DTMF_INST/ARB_INST/n_36
                -cell INVX4 -name {{cell1 cell2}} -newNetName {{net1 net2}}en-
                dECO

                vim <FILE1>All operations performed by ECO Commands are logged
                in <FILE1>.

Related Information
              * initECO

